      "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"introduction img-head\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"header\"\u003e\n    \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"App Icon\" /\u003e\n    \u003ch3\u003eWelcome to Event Planner\u003c/h3\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003csection\u003e\n    \u003ch4\u003eOverview\u003c/h4\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003e\n      A GenAI-based assistant that helps plan strategic go-to-market events by interpreting the company and product context, generating the agenda, crafting event names and taglines, and comparing against real-world benchmarks.\n    \u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/section\u003e\n\n  \u003csection\u003e\n    \u003ch4\u003eInput\u003c/h4\u003e\n    \u003cul\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eCompany name\u003c/strong\u003e: The company hosting or leading the event (required)\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eLead Industry\u003c/strong\u003e: The industry/domain the event aligns with (required)\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eEvent Location\u003c/strong\u003e: Geographic or virtual location (e.g., \"San Francisco\", \"Virtual\") (required)\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eEvent Type\u003c/strong\u003e: Type of event (e.g., \"Product Launch\", \"Product Demo\") (required)\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eEvent Lead Name\u003c/strong\u003e: Point of contact for the event (optional)\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eProduct Name\u003c/strong\u003e: The featured product or service (optional)\u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\n  \u003c/section\u003e\n\n  \u003csection\u003e\n    \u003ch4\u003eOutput\u003c/h4\u003e\n    \u003cul\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eEvent Agenda:\u003c/strong\u003e A detailed schedule with sessions, speakers, and themes\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eEvent Name \u0026 Tagline:\u003c/strong\u003e Creative branding suggestions aligned with the domain\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eContext Summary:\u003c/strong\u003e A table summarizing the input context used for planning\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eBenchmark Events:\u003c/strong\u003e Comparable real-world events with source URLs for inspiration\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eEach output category is presented in a separate table for clarity and easy navigation\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\n  \u003c/section\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n",
